<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَيَحْرُمُ إِحْدَادٌ عَلَى مَيِّتٍ غَيْرِ زَوْجٍ:</span> فَوْقَ ثَلَاثٍ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَيَجِبُ:</span> عَلَى زَوْجَةِ مَيِّتٍ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَيُبَاحُ:</span> لِبَائِنٍ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَهُوَ:</span> تَرْكُ زِينَةٍ، وَطِيبٍ، وَكُلِّ مَا يَدْعُو إِلَى جِمَاعِهَا وَيُرَغِّبُ فِي النَّظَرِ إِلَيْهَا.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>- وَيَحْرُمُ - بِلَا حَاجَةٍ -: تَحَوُّلُهَا مِنْ مَسْكَنٍ وَجَبَتْ فِيهِ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَلَهَا الخُرُوجُ لِحَاجَتِهَا:</span> نَهَاراً.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>- وَمَنْ مَلَكَ أَمَةً يُوطَأُ مِثْلُهَا مِنْ أَيِّ شَخْصٍ كَانَ؛<span class="c5"> حَرُمَ عَلَيْهِ وَطْؤُهَا وَمُقَدِّمَاتُهُ قَبْلَ اسْتِبْرَاءِ:</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>-<span class="c5"> حَامِلٍ:</span> بِوَضْعٍ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَمَنْ تَحِيضُ:</span> بِحَيْضَةٍ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَآيِسَةٍ وَصَغِيرَةٍ:</span> بِشَهْرٍ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>